open-source.s9.p:
OSS dependencies change between App and server releases as we update packages for security, compatibility, and
  features. The list of components and versions is therefore not static. This notice will be updated periodically;
  see the &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date above.

ai-disclaimer.s2.p:
AI systems generate responses based on patterns in training data and your inputs. They can produce incorrect, incomplete,
  outdated, biased, or misleading information. This phenomenon is commonly known as a &ldquo;hallucination.&rdquo;
  AI output may appear confident even when it is wrong.
